title: 13-10-2015 | Helping older drivers: International award for QUT optometry researcher (Queensland University of Technology) ...
text: ( Source : Queensland University of Technology ) 13 October 2015 One of the world's leading experts on visual impairment, ageing and driving, QUT 's Professor Joanne Wood , has won the ' Nobel Prize ' of international optometry for her work.
